urity_Vision_2030_03032025.docx\n# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\npython -m media_monitor coverage-24h \\\n  --client \"Phosphorus\" \\\n  --campaign \"IoT Security Vision 2030\" \\\n  --date \"3rd March 2025\" \\\n  --items-file coverage_items.json\n\n# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n# COMMAND 3 – Excel Tracker\n# Output: output/tracker/ADMC_clients_Phosphorustracker.xlsx\n# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\npython -m media_monitor tracker update \\\n  --client \"Phosphorus\" \\\n  --entries-file tracker_entries.json\n\n# ── Interactive mode (no JSON file needed) ─────────────────────────────────\npython -m media_monitor snapshot --url \"https://...\" --client \"Denodo\" --magazine \"TechNews\"\npython -m media_monitor coverage-24h --client \"Denodo\" --campaign \"Q1 Launch\"\npython -m media_monitor tracker update --client \"Denodo\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Setup Checklist\n\n```\nassets/\n├── active_logo.png              ← Drop your Active/ADMC logo here\n└── client_logos/\n    ├── phosphorus.png           ← Named exactly as client name (lowercase)\n    ├── denodo.png\n    └── netscout.png\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🗂️ Output File Examples\n\n| Command | Output File |\n|---|---|\n| `snapshot` | `ADMC_Phosphorus_CXO_Insight_ME_03032025.docx` |\n| `coverage-24h` | `ADMC_Phosphorus_IoT_Security_Vision_2030_03032025.docx` |\n| `tracker update` | `ADMC_clients_Phosphorustracker.xlsx` |\n\n---\n\n> **Key notes:**\n> - Drop logos in `assets/client_logos/` named as `clientname.png` (lowercase)\n> - Drop the Active logo at `assets/active_logo.png`\n> - Both logos auto-appear at the top of every document\n> - All 3 commands work interactively without a JSON file (just omit `--items-file` / `--entries-file`)\n> - Chrome must be installed for screenshot capture (ChromeDriver auto-downloads)"
